org.apache.juneau.http.header

Class BasicEntityTagArrayHeader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.http.BasicHeader
      • org.apache.juneau.http.header.BasicEntityTagArrayHeader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Header, NameValuePair
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IfMatch, IfNoneMatch

    public class BasicEntityTagArrayHeader
extends BasicHeader
    Category of headers that consist of a comma-delimited list of entity validator values.

    Example

    If-Match: "xyzzy" If-Match: "xyzzy", "r2d2xxxx", "c3piozzzz" If-Match: *

    • Hypertext Transfer Protocol -- HTTP/1.1
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
